James Azania, Lokoja Suspected political thugs during the early hours of Monday, burnt down the Kofi Social Democratic Party (SDP) secretariat, in Lokoja, the capital. The SDP secretariat is located adjacent to Lokoja local government secretariat, around the Paparanda Square. The SDP secretariat was earlier attacked on Sunday, as yet unknown persons destroyed its windows and doors, while banners, posters and other campaign materials at the secretariat were also vandalized. The party had earlier alleged of ongoing plans to attack the convoy of the SDP governorship candidate, Barr. Natasha Akpoti, adding that the unfolding events confirmed its outcry, ahead of Saturdayâ€™s poll.